#* Shakespeare, ''Much Ado About Nothing'':
#*: ''Art thou the '''slave''' that with thy breath hast kill'd/ Mine innocent child?''
# {{lb|en|figuratively}} One who has no the power of resistance (to something), one who surrenders to or is under the [[domination]] (of something_.
#: {{ux|en|a '''slave''' to passion, to strong drink, or to ambition}}
# {{lb|en|BDSM}} A [[submissive]] partner in a [[BDSM]] relationship who ([[consensually]]) [[submit]]s to (sexually and/or personally) serving one or more masters or mistresses.
#: {{hypernyms|en|sub}}
